{"tid":907444,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人會瞓瞓吓扎醒左 心跳加快","createTime":"2018-11-18T19:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T04:24:46.000Z","uid":140022,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8db9618a94bdfb3bc6049b482b424ef194816854","tid":907444,"uid":140022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T19:26:35.000Z","msg":"呢排成日瞓瞓吓覺扎醒左<br />\n然之後心跳跳得好快 1秒跳成幾下 以為自己會死<br />\n即刻坐返起身 飲啖水 坐30秒左右就正常返<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d29fd5ebf05c674c2ce2f29f71a05d34176ee29","tid":907444,"uid":140022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T19:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0ffd133eab129e58c0b1d205a57ef0ab343729","tid":907444,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T19:32:31.000Z","msg":"試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲試過發夢比人練住條頸抖唔到氣，就黎疾息，然後醒左果幾秒都係抖唔到氣，放鬆返個人又無野，果次真係以為會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec508d88b8823997fb728ec81f1566edd24617b0","tid":907444,"uid":140022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa0ffd133eab129e58c0b1d205a57ef0ab343729","tid":907444,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T19:32:31.000Z","msg":"試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲試過發夢比人練住條頸抖唔到氣，就黎疾息，然後醒左果幾秒都係抖唔到氣，放鬆返個人又無野，果次真係以為會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T19:33:50.000Z","msg":"有冇睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個種感覺好似會猝死咁"},{"pid":"b9612f118e901dae05e92f9e1bc8c415a74ed977","tid":907444,"uid":319